title: Martinu Bohuslav - Julietta (1964 cond. Jaroslav Krombholc) m4a
description:
I couldn't find this opera on any torrent or streaming websites, so I ended up buying it - thought I'd share :)


Julietta is an opera in three acts by Martinu Bohuslav. It's what can probably be called his real operatic masterpiece. Martinu was an extremely prolific Czech composer who has, sadly, not received much attention. He lived in the early 1900's.

This performance is quite good.

Main Personnel:

Conductor: Jaroslav Krombholc
Chorus Master: Milan Maly
Julietta: Maria Tauberova
Michel: Ivo Zidek
Performed by the Prague National Theatre Chorus and Orchestra

This is my first torrent, hope y'all enjoy it!
